high_descs: Go to the kitchen counter to the right of you.
Grab the coffee mug that's behind the glove.
Walk to the fridge to your left.
Place the mug in the fridge, then grab it out of the fridge.
Walk to the shelving unit to the left of the kitchen counter.
Place the mug on the second shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Cool down a mug for showcasing on a shelf.

high_descs: Go to the middle of the island and turn right.
Pick up the white coffee mug behind the hand shaped decor.
Turn left to go to the refrigerator on the left.
Chill the coffee mug on the top shelf in the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn left and left again at the counter and go to the wooden shelf on the opposite side of the kitchen.
Place the coffee mug on the second shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled mug on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the counter near the tomato and white mug.
Pick the white mug up from the counter.
Go left and then turn left to face the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge, shut the door and then open the door again and pick the mug up again.
Go left and then go left again and turn to the right to face the brown shelves.
Put the mug down on the right side of the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on a shelf.
